THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS:

Porter2 Stemmer Implementation
Original Author: Sean Massung
Modified by: Alex Towell
Based on: http://snowball.tartarus.org/algorithms/english/stemmer.html
License: Compatible with GPL v2 (original algorithm is public domain)

The Porter2 stemming algorithm itself is in the public domain as described
by Martin Porter. The implementation has been adapted for use within the
algebraic framework of this library while maintaining compatibility with
the original algorithm specification.

